# Safety-first: ignore EVERYTHING by default so the private source,
# build script, and node_modules can never be committed by accident.
*

# ...and explicitly allow ONLY the published, obfuscated artifact:
!index.html
!.gitignore

# ...plus the static PWA assets that must ship next to it so the app is
# installable ("Pin to taskbar"). Each is listed by name on purpose — never
# use a wildcard here, or the private source could slip through.
!manifest.webmanifest
!sw.js
!favicon.ico
!icon-192.png
!icon-512.png
!icon-512-maskable.png
